{"type": "article", "id": 47508, "title": "这个竹制名片盒，想让你礼貌优雅地递名片｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-22T22:56:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 162, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171122205253dkcM0hsuvXKxWLT2.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Boarding Furniture by Studio Kunsik </h3><p>瑞典设计工作室 Kunsik 以马尔默的 Stapelbäddsparken 滑板公园为灵感，创作了“滑板”家具系列，滑板弯道的流线元素被融入家具造型中，当然这并非只是凹造型的作品，它同时还兼顾了传统家具所拥有的功能与细节，包括沙发、边桌与茶几等。&nbsp;</p><p>Kunsik 的创始人是韩裔设计师 Kunsik Choi，这组家具也是他为阿迪达斯 Original 在首尔的旗舰店量身设计的家具，希望能够用家具的流线造型呼应品牌的运动主题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711222054187eWyt2pgn8IcHwlX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205418It6AjQMbFWcoGXSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205418CpGhRe4EfIsKOdq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711222054187V1YHNAmtO2kFq40.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205419gdQcKGDao9nJy1YA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205419BSlLCIF6btcj8N5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shapes Post by Deep Yellow</h3><p>Deep Yellow 是一个小型设计工作室，他们最为人熟知的作品是一系列平面设计海报，专注于表现几何构图、阴影及色彩过渡之间的美学关系。尽管都是抽象的几何图形，却有着非常漂亮的构图和迷人的色彩退晕效果。售价 12 美元，<a href=\"http://deepyellow.net/shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205659XMBpK136zbcSNjdV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205659fGNFv6WQCydocXm8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205659FaLYnDAgBjx5KCU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205700Nwk9u1nxDYE2PVyl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205700hI7nXcyGLCNx5Zgi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205700pLghWy3v5nCVIX6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.redbubble.com/people/deepyellow/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deep Yellow</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Slide Bamboo Card Case by TreAsia Design</h3><p>TreAsia 是一个台湾原创设计师品牌，擅长于贴近人心的细腻设计。这款名片盒采用竹材制成，设计师思考的是使用者在交换名片及介绍自己身份时的得体，如何礼貌、轻松、优雅地将名片递给对方？设计师为名片盒设计了一个可以滑动的盖子，提供黑色、深钛色以及铜绿色三种选择，轻轻滑动盖子，再将名片滑出，是一个连贯的过程，也透露着一种自信。售价 55 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/slide%EF%BD%9Cbamboo-card-case-tad-07-04-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205837L8edFcMVSkvb0XOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205838LmjnOEyGhrp5Voaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205838KlNu7OpbqGQeAxkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205838eopfsEh5FPyraudO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017112220583808irX2EvTlCu39St.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.treasia-design.com/lifestyle-accessories\" rel=\"nofollow\">TreAsia Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Gaia is a self by Aric Snee</h3><p>Gaia 是一款自动浇水器，非常适合放在厨房中种植一些小型草药或者迷你植物。它来自设计师兼艺术家 Aric Snee 的创意，在工厂、工作室等各种地方从事玻璃工艺制作超过 15 年时间，亦有雕塑专业的学习背景。</p><p>Gaia 手工吹制的磨砂玻璃底座恰是 Aric 的优势，他将整个瓶身的造型描述为“斯堪的纳维亚风格”，确保植物拥有最好的生长环境。尼龙芯用来连接水和土壤，确保植物所需的适宜水量。如果养好的话，放在家中也不失为一个自然装饰。售价 59 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/gaia-aric-snee-07-28-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205935PcFIyULe6K5G9fCS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205936sV4nibocHhmtOFQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205936QJ7fsSiwB8ZK5rWt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205936mqDXl8Id52RfO1xN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205937jxTob0Rq2lhIW6Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122205936jkzMEONnxIQq03W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/gaia-aric-snee-07-28-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Beerdy Bottle Opener by Peleg Design</h3><p>人们常说，狗是人类最好的朋友。我们曾多次介绍过的以色列工作室 Peleg Design 也在设想，这个“最好的朋友”是否能帮我们开启一瓶啤酒？不管是独自在家中，还是与众人欢聚在 party 上，设计师希望这款名为 Beerdy 的小狗造型开瓶器都能够成为你的伙伴，帮你撬开最欢愉的时刻。售价 12 美元，<a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/shop/beerdy.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210434fbDB5gHYuW8vPsAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210035Xn3B0hDYr968JTsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210036YID9vAQPFSuK5c6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210036zr5kd6ScIbHtJ7Yq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210036lS3v0Cczqh4QHRxG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Peleg Design</figcaption></figure></div><h3>BREW V60 GIFTSET BLACK by Tom Dixon</h3><p>BREW V60 是一个为入门的咖啡爱好者准备的咖啡礼盒，造型时尚，延续了 Tom Dixon 一贯线条简练现代的风格。如果你对时下这波冰滴咖啡的热潮感兴趣，它会是个简单易上手的选择。一个像镜子一样的 V60 咖啡滴壶加上两个意式浓缩咖啡杯，表面镀上黑色镜面 PVD 涂层，内层则为不锈钢，试图赋予每日清晨的一杯咖啡仪式感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210116kvt2z7UqWy0SuAgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.824000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210117CoyYBk0EieGtVdlZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.824286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171122210116Rze1h0VLykKlxvCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.824176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：Tom Dixon</p>"}